textContent:
Feeling scared and hanging on - 

Arielle crosses a boundary and went to far by circling back and ask what was coming up 

The flip floppedness
The boy who cried Wolf 
The going back and going forward

Based on experience with own romantic relationships.. and it's not healthy 

There are some bearings on my life 

Feeling the terrain shifting ... Back to go forward is not what Arielle wants to do and going back opened up that portal.... The going back and forth is not one to be part of 

Voice on Friday - at a critical point. The paradox of wanting to be there and not wanting to do that dance 

Is there a reorganizing for how time is being spent? And implications for how time is being utilized? 

I've made a decision to walk away from IDG, Porsche work, brought in Carly... And confidence in figuring out fina financially
